sentences: Niven became the manager of Guns N' Roses, serving from 1986 to 1991.

According to a 1991 cover story by Rolling Stone magazine, frontman Axl Rose forced the dismissal of Niven (against the wishes of some of his band-mates) by refusing to complete the albums until he was replaced.
He currently co-hosts Westwood One's Rock Talk With Mitch Lafon with rock journalist Mitch Lafon.
